The Role:

Entegris is seeking an experienced Analytical Scientist who will work on cutting edge techniques to push our metrology capabilities for our specialty gases products to the next level. Come help design, deliver, and optimize the products that help produce some of the most important semiconductor devices in the world! You will develop new analytical methods, lead various analytical capability improvements, maintain analytical equipment, and develop new products/ improving current products. Additionally, you will support customer requests and work closely and effectively with Sales, Marketing, Research and Engineering. This role is based in Danbury, CT.

In this role you will:
